OL,3,CHealthcare assistants to go on strike
OL,4,Cfor seven days
OL,6,FHundreds of healthcare assistants on
OL,7,FTeesside are going on strike for a
OL,8,Ffurther seven days, a union has said.
OL,10,FUnison has said the workers, who are
OL,11,Femployed by North Tees and Hartlepool
OL,12,FNHS Foundation Trust, will walk out
OL,13,Ffor a fourth time next week in their
OL,14,Fdispute over wage rates and back pay.
OL,16,FThe latest action will begin with an
OL,17,Finitial five-day strike from Monday 10
OL,18,FJune to Saturday 15 June.
